		<title>Custom AI chips, 3.5 gigawatts, and a quiet SEC clause: the Broadcom deal explained</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/broadcom-custom-ai-chips-google-anthropic-deal/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dashveenjit Kaur]]></dc:creator>
