<p>The post <a href="https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/enterprise-data-resilience-ai-era-backup/">Enterprise data resilience is no longer about backup. AI broke the old rules.</a> appeared first on <a href="https://techwireasia.com">TechWire Asia</a>.</p>
